---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about Denis Seloy — full-stack developer and open-source enthusiast."
	pubDate={new Date('2024-01-01')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Hi! I'm <strong>Denis Seloy</strong>, a full-stack developer with a passion for building
		thoughtful, high-quality web applications. I enjoy turning complex problems into simple,
		elegant solutions and I take pride in writing clean, maintainable code.
	</p>

	<p>
		My primary stack includes <strong>TypeScript</strong>, <strong>React</strong>, and
		<strong>Node.js</strong>, though I'm always curious to pick up new tools whenever they make
		sense for the project. I've worked on everything from small side-projects to larger
		applications, and I'm comfortable across the full lifecycle — from system design to deployment.
	</p>

	<p>
		When I'm not coding I enjoy contributing to open-source projects, reading about software
		architecture, and exploring new frameworks. I believe great software is built through
		continuous learning and collaboration.
	</p>

	<p>
		Feel free to explore my <a href="/projects">projects</a>, read my
		<a href="/blog">blog posts</a>, or reach out via
		<a href="https://github.com/denisseloyizz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>. I'd
		love to connect!
	</p>
</Layout>
